  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bc0\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9c\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bcb\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u00a0- \u0b9c\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb0",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna-led government needs to re-emerge - Jagat Kumara",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The government led by Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has failed. Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna Member of Parliament Jagat Kumara said that we will insist to the President that the government led by Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna should be re-emerged or the general election should be held quickly.",
        "A couple of bad decisions by the Budujana Peramuna-led government put the two-thirds majority power of the people in question.",
        "In order to weaken the government, the attack carried out on the Khali protestors on the 9th of May had serious consequences.",
        "Most of the members of the Podujana Peramuna supported the government led by United National Party leader Ranil Wickremesinghe to solve the basic problems faced by the people of the country.",
        "The government led by Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has not yet solved the problems faced by the people of the country.",
        "The crises are intensifying day by day and not abating. The Prime Minister acts like a spokesman for crises.",
        "Majority of members of Podujana Peramuna insisted during the committee meeting held last month under the chairmanship of the President that the Prime Minister of Podujana Peramuna should be chosen.",
        "The President personally mentioned various issues regarding the appointment of Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "We will insist to the President that a Podujana Peramuna-led government should be formed or general elections should be held quickly.",
        "He said that it can be observed that the fuel problem has been aggravated and the measures affecting the national existence are being carried out."
      ],
